# Replication Files for [Rebel Groups and Human Rights Violations]

## Overview
This project replicates the analysis of [Rebel Groups and Human Rights Violations]. The analysis investigates how rebel origins shape HR abuses. 

## Folder Structure
- `datasets/`: Contains all raw data files and the merged datasets used in the analysis.
- `do_files/`: Contains Stata Files that replicate the analysis. 

## Data Source
The datasets used in this project are sourced from [Forge Data, Human Rights Abuses Datasets, Non State Actors datasets

